question: Show me Airbus aircrafts and Boeing aircrafts with 180 seats.
sql_query1:
SELECT Manufactures.aircraftModel 
FROM Manufactures
WHERE (Manufactures.manufacturers = "Airbus" OR Manufactures.manufacturers = "Boeing") AND Manufactures.numberOfSeats = 180
sql_query2:
SELECT Manufactures.aircraftModel 
FROM Manufactures
WHERE Manufactures.manufacturers = "Airbus" OR Manufactures.manufacturers = "Boeing" AND Manufactures.numberOfSeats = 180
interpretation1: What Airbus aircrafts have 180 seats and what Boeing aircrafts have the same number of seats?
interpretation2: Provide a list of all Airbus aircrafts and also provide a list of Boeing aircrafts with 180 seats.
